					<MadeStyleItem width="10.2rem" height="5.1rem" imgWidth="4.99rem" />
					<Flex flexDirection="column">
						<MadeStyleItem width="3.4rem" height="1.7rem" imgWidth="1.4rem" />
						<MadeStyleItem width="3.4rem" height="1.7rem" imgWidth="1.4rem" />
						<MadeStyleItem width="3.4rem" height="1.7rem" imgWidth="1.4rem" />
					</Flex>
				</Flex>
			</Box>

	)
}
